name: Generative Interference
description:
This piece is a viewer for objkt #218752 (Gen Rings). Fetchs the current owners of objkt #218752 and displays the variation based on wallet address for each owner. Created with p5.js | @atimtay | linktr.ee/atimtakus

This pieces creates interference patterns also known as Moire patterns by overlapping two squares. The wallet address of the owner determines the amount of rotation,scale and line thickness | @atimtay | linktr.ee/atimtakus
